    tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts,project,unit coverage for command and renderer registration
    tests/unit/extensions-runtime.spec.ts,project,runtime wrapper coverage for active command and renderer override registries
    tests/unit/output.spec.ts,project,coverage for renderer and command-result override formatting behavior
